%h4 Complete Catalogue
%ul
  - data.book.editions.each do |edition|
    - if edition.name != "Online"
      - if edition.file_size_mb != nil
        %li= link_to "#{edition.name} (#{edition.file_size_mb} MB)", edition.link, :target => "blank", :class => "no-smoothState"
      - else
        %li= link_to "#{edition.name}", edition.link, :target => "blank", :class => "no-smoothState"
:markdown
  Each of these alternative formats includes the complete catalogue text, the top view image for each object, all the indices, and the map.
%hr
%h4 Object Data
%ul
  - data.book.other_resources.each do |resource|
    - if resource.type == "data"
      - if resource.file_size_mb != nil
        %li= link_to "#{resource.name} (#{resource.file_size_mb} MB)", resource.link, :target => "blank", :class => "no-smoothState"
      - else
        %li= link_to "#{resource.name}", resource.link, :target => "blank", :class => "no-smoothState"
:markdown
  The object data, available in two formats, includes key information from each
  of the catalogue objects.
%hr
